  "notificationScheduleMonthlyReached": "Monthly target already reached ({completed}/{target}). Extra rep, extra momentum.|You've nailed your monthly goal ({completed}/{target}). This is elite consistency.|Monthly target: done ({completed}/{target}). Everything now is exponential growth.|Monthly goal already crushed ({completed}/{target}). Bonus reps deepen the groove.",
